  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ever dreamt of putting a pineapple down a pirate ship while your friends go full sabotage with sharks and exploding barrels? Fruit Golf turns every swing into a chaotic, laugh-out-loud party in VR. It’s a game that the whole family will go bananas fore!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras/6231250eb28c5c334e16fabd8654282a.avif?t=1750308884\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras_big/6231250eb28c5c334e16fabd8654282a.avif?t=1750308884 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fruit Golf is will be launching in Early Access!</strong> We’re just getting started! Follow our progress and check out the roadmap at  to see what juicy updates are coming next!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras/a365b404e162e59528714b474a9d0b1b.avif?t=1750308884\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras_big/a365b404e162e59528714b474a9d0b1b.avif?t=1750308884 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VR SHOWDOWN:</strong> Go head-to-head in VR! Online or in-person, take turns golfing and sabotaging.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE GOLFING GATHERING:</strong> One headset, many saboteurs! Friends join FREE on phones  to wreak fruity havoc.😈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SOLO PRACTICE:</strong> Hone your swing, conquer challenges, and enjoy the hilarious physics of Fruit Golf<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras/7e15493ef9ad4eec92bf8bbd78c06c08.avif?t=1750308884\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras_big/7e15493ef9ad4eec92bf8bbd78c06c08.avif?t=1750308884 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pick Your Perfect Fruit!</strong> Every fruit isn't just a ball, it's a strategy! Each has unique physics to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras/c7b9e1f2452acf68f683f5c2bbfa94ca.avif?t=1750308884\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras_big/c7b9e1f2452acf68f683f5c2bbfa94ca.avif?t=1750308884 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlocks & Customization!</strong> Style your swing! Complete challenges to unlock gear and turn every round into a fruit-smashing fashion statement.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras/d06aa5dcfbc4e4fe2c976c6bea7c6445.avif?t=1750308884\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras_big/d06aa5dcfbc4e4fe2c976c6bea7c6445.avif?t=1750308884 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras/efb02b6b97d706ed35afce7ecb6c8767.avif?t=1750308884\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/406890/extras_big/efb02b6b97d706ed35afce7ecb6c8767.avif?t=1750308884 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNIQUE FRUIT PHYSICS!</strong> 🍍 Discover how each fruit plays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CREATIVE OBSTACLES!</strong> 🦈 Floppy Sharks, Dust Devils, Dynamite, Zombie Arms, Mouse Traps, and Many More!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLIMITED FUN!</strong> 🗺️ Themed courses where you can mix and match obstacles.</p>",
